title: Nora to Oujo to Noraneko Heart (Nora, Princess, and Stray Cat)
synopsis: Nora Handa is a boy who lives with Shachi Yuuri, who was adopted by his mother. With everyone supporting, the two of them grew up healthily even after their parents passed away. Shachi, who likes Nora the most, wakes him up every morning.
